{"tid":1644890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，跪求創新再突破的方式！（和理非）","createTime":"2019-10-10T16:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T17:04:57.000Z","uid":82725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60aed955ab5d499cd33ce4f030baf50b8faa1a5a","tid":1644890,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武我就核爆都唔會割，<br />\n但唔可以日日都靠勇武抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n        <span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家唔好唔記得，香港人係善忘，好快忘記初心抗爭，比政府推反啲問題落示威者身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地可以唔信，但我身邊好多人已經由淺黃到退出，我深信各位巴絲一定會感受到，連日嚟勇武已經令社會傾斜，民主運動真唔可以全失民心留係同温層打飛機，根本唔需要咩休息日！和理非一早收工成晚係屋企hea,種休息乜嘢？休息係留俾勇武巴絲</span><br />\n<br />\n自問唔係勇武巴絲，請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n目前已有：<br />\n1-人鏈<br />\n2-人鏈攻山頂<br />\n3-摺紙鶴<br />\n4-絕食<br />\n5-200萬人遊行<br />\n6-連儂牆粉筆<br />\n7-和理塞<br />\n8-激光派對<br />\n9-社區對話（勉強算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10-參選做選民<br />\n11-籌款捐錢登報<br />\n12-宣傳動畫文宣<br />\n13-獻花/紙花<br />\n14-民間記招<br />\n15-藍黃app<br />\n16-10點唱榮光<br />\n17-10點窗邊一呼百應<br />\n18-唱詩歌淨化空氣<br />\n19-撳錢日<br />\n（暫時諗到咁多）<br />\n<br />\nEtc.<br />\n[url]後生都唔戴口罩，不如整個ig 口罩challenge啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請出招啊各位巴打絲打</span><br />\n先獻醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得就嚟萬聖節，可以搞返一個星期抗爭舞會面具周，只要人人都帶，就唔會覺得奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而唔帶面具先係異類，口罩我估好多人覺得焗先唔帶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGxLQv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGxLQv6.jpg&h=a58c2a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，寫銀紙！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲20蚊100蚊寫曬<br />\n光復香港🇭🇰時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540ebf0dec1a8aa0bf40c13c497064edc3bdaef5","tid":1644890,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8427eb860ed2edd1393a235869354da11af8aff2","tid":1644890,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"另類連儂牆 家家戶戶都知道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ad1a5819d6923da301fbe509822dcbfb5ce799f","tid":1644890,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />創意嘅連登仔去咗邊？"},{"pid":"9b6148f0716ddc1dde7215514c8915952e134ee2","tid":1644890,"uid":82725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"如果早上進行抗爭，將會打破現時運動樽頸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}